file.name: content-types.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Swagger Petstore
  license:
    name: MIT
servers:
  - url: http://petstore.swagger.io/v1
paths:
  /pets/{petId}:
    parameters:
      - name: petId
        in: path
        required: true
        description: The id of the pet to retrieve
        schema:
          type: string
    get:
      summary: Info for a specific pet
      operationId: showPetById
      tags:
        - pets
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Expected response to a valid request
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                title: 'Without parameter'
                type: object
            application/json; profile=custom:
              schema:
                title: 'With profile'
                type: object
            text/*:
              schema:
                title: 'Text wildcard'
                type: string
            '*/*':
              schema:
                title: 'Accept everything'
                type: object
    patch:
      summary: Update for a specific pet
      operationId: updatePetById
      tags:
        - pets
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                title: 'Without parameter'
                type: object
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              title: 'Without parameter'
              type: object
          application/json; profile=custom:
            schema:
              title: 'With profile'
              type: object
          text/*:
            schema:
              title: 'Text wildcard'
              type: string
          '*/*':
            schema:
              title: 'Accept everything'
              type: object
